check in your mc the version of python with

python 

then ensure to use pip
with 


sudo python -m ensurepip --default-pip

you must use sudo and provide the password

then:

sudo python -m pip install mypackage

where 'mypackage' can be any module like 'wakeonlan'

you can also select a specific version with:

python -m pip install SomePackage==1.0.4    